  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/secretaries-commerce-and-energy-lead-clean-energy-trade-mission-china">Secretaries of Commerce and Energy to Lead Clean Energy Trade Mission to China</a></span>
