  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p><i>This post <a href="http://www.wri.org/blog/how-us-china-cooperation-can-expand-clean-energy-development">originally appeared</a> on WRI&#8217;s Insights blog:</i></p>

<p>One year ago, the United States and China declared in their <a href="http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2013/04/207465.htm">Joint Statement on Climate Change</a> that ‚Äúforceful, nationally appropriate action by the United States and China‚Äîincluding large-scale cooperative action‚Äîis more critical than ever. Such action is crucial both to contain climate change and to set the kind of powerful example that can inspire the world.‚Äù</p></div>
